        public static <M,​T> KafkaPollArraySupplier.Mapped<T> kafkaArray​(String description,
                                                                      Class<M> classT,
                                                                      Class<T> componentClass,
                                                                      Function<M,​T> toGet,
                                                                      String... topics)
        Creates a step that returns array of values which are calculated by data of read messages.

        It is not necessary to define topics. If there is no topic defined then value of the property KafkaDefaultTopicsForPollProperty.DEFAULT_TOPICS_FOR_POLL is used.
        Type Parameters:
        M - is a type of deserialized message
        T - is a type of item of array
        Parameters:
        description - is description of value to get
        classT - is a class of a value to deserialize a message from topics
        componentClass - is a class of array item
        toGet - describes how to get desired value
        topics - are topics to get messages from
        Returns:
        an instance of KafkaPollArraySupplier.Mapped
